    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<h1>\n    Funkcja wykładnicza\n</h1>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n    Przypomnijmy sobie bardzo krótko podstawowe działania na potęgach.\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"question\">\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Przyjrzyj się poznanym wcześniej wzorom i uzupełnij brakujące pola.\n    "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n            \\(a^n\\cdot a^k=a^{n+k}\\)\n        </div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(2^3\\cdot 2^4=2\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input11\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n            \\(a^n: a^k=a^{n-k}\\)\n        </div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(3^{11}: 3^6=3\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input12\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n            \\(\\left(a^n\\right)^k=a^{n\\cdot k}\\)\n        </div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(\\left(3^4\\right)^5=3\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input13\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(25^6=5\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input14\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n            \\(a^{-n}=\\frac{1}{a^n}\\)\n        </div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(\\frac{1}{8}=2\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input15\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n            \\(a^{\\frac{1}{n}}=\\sqrt[n]{a}\\)\n        </div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(\\sqrt[5]{3}=3\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input16\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"200px\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"fixed_width\" data-width=\"300px\">\n<span class=\"myequation\">\n                \\(\\sqrt[5]{9}=3\\)\n                <sup>\n<input id=\"table_input17\" placeholder=\"???\" type=\"text\"/>\n</sup>\n</span>\n</div>\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n<div class=\"success hidden\" id=\"success_question5\">\n        Doskonale!\n    </div>\n</p>"
    },
